{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"z3-quiz-7","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"专题集训","title":"专题集训三 第7题","difficulty":4,"tags":["代数式","代换"],"content":"若代数式 $2x^2 - 4x - 5$ 的值为 $7$，则 $x^2 - 2x - 2$ 的值为______","steps":[{"title":"利用整体思想","content":"由 $2x^2 - 4x - 5 = 7$ 得 $2(x^2 - 2x) = 12$，即 $x^2 - 2x = 6$\n所以 $x^2 - 2x - 2 = 6 - 2 = 4$","formula":"\\text{答案：}4"}]},"id":"z3-quiz-7"},"__N_SSG":true}